item.title: 个人主页
item.description: YINGQI TANG tyq is currently studying for a master’s degree in the University of Electronic Science and Technology of China, Chengdu, China and received a bachelor’s degree from Chongqing University in 2019. His research is image processing based on deep learning, including intelligent transportation and video analysis.
